McARRAY project Change Log

## [Unreleased]

## [0.2.0 ] - 2016-10-05

## [0.1.8] - 2014-11-17

### Changes

- expose binauralmasking configuration to avoid dependencies on internals
  This is to avoid a dependency on FastBinauralMasking
- WIPP a necessary dependency for dependant projects
- Detection threshold moved down to +6dB from +20dB
- Added a function to calculate array BW
- Some public methods to acces distances and coordinate vectors in Array Description
- Propagate ArrayDescription to the rest of the code
- Added a class to manage Array Description
  This class stores the ID, the NAME and position in 3D
  space for each element of the array.
  It can also be used to compute distances between array elements
  in cartesian space.

- Contributors: Jordi Adell

## [0.1.7] - 2014-11-10

### Changes

- Including BinauralLocalisation instead of the old SoundLocalisation

- Contributors: Jordi Adell

